iates to create stronger relationships with each other outside of the workplace the calamos cares team has volunteered at the northern illinois food bank and participated in both the march of dimes march for babies and the american cancer society relay for life take our daughters and sons to work day calamos participates in the annual take our daughters and sons to work day which helps bring children into the workplace to understand their parents daily activities as well as explore personal career choices naperville wine festival calamos is the host and one of the lead sponsors of the annual naperville wine festival held in august at citygate centre a portion of the proceeds from the naperville wine festival are donated to the naperville area humane society and alexs lemonade stand foundation naperville area chamber of commerce calamos has been a member of the naperville area chamber of commerce since  the company sponsors the chambers annual economic forecast breakfast and the organizations inaugural gala where past board members are thanked for their service to the community and current board members are introduced including a representative from calamos choose dupage calamos is a leader in regional economic development through choose dupage an organization that drives economic development in dupage county by leveraging the areas growth for the benefit of county businesses and residents john calamos sr is on the board of directors for the organization why calamos company cafeteria calamos encourages associates to eat together our gourmet cafeteria offers daily entrees salad bar sandwich station makeyourown pizza and more “best places to live”  money magazine rated naperville il as a best place to live because of great job opportunities topnotch schools safe streets economic strength and more to learn more about naperville visit napervillenet calamos green building the  square foot office building is a firstclass stateoftheart headquarters one of the first privatel